## New Required Slots

| Slot | Description | Before |
|------|-------------|--------|
| [intent](file:///c:/Users/Kevin/Projects/personal_projects/DuoTrak_v1.1/backend/app/services/goal_chat/slot_tracker.py#20-25) | habit, milestone, target-date | ✅ Same |
| `success_definition` | What does success look like | ✅ Same |
| `accountability_type` | photo, video, voice, check_in, task_completion | 🔄 Was `accountability_mode` (generic text) |
| `tasks` | Key tasks with partner review settings | ✅ Same |
| `user_summary` | **NEW** — AI-written narrative of user's goals, motivations, schedule, reservations | 🆕 Replaces `availability` + `time_budget` as separate slots |
| `deadline` / `review_cycle` | Conditional on intent | ✅ Same |

## Verification

- Test fresh chat with "I want to learn Python in 3 months"
- Verify AI suggests voice reflections (learning goal)
- Test "I want to wake up at 7am every day" → AI suggests check-in window
- Test "I want to go to the gym 4x/week" → AI suggests photo proof
- Confirm summary includes user_summary narrative
